high_descs: Turn right and walk over to the toilet, then turn right and walk around the toilet to the left side of the counter.
Pick up the bar of soap out of the left sink.
Turn around to look at the toilet.
Put the bar of soap on top of the toilet tank.
Turn left and walk forward, then turn left to face the counter.
Pick up the bar of soap off of the counter.
Turn left and walk forward, then turn left to face the toilet.
Put the bar of soap on top of the toilet tank next to the bar of soap that is already there.
anns.task_desc: Move two bars of soap to the toilet tank.

high_descs: Back up, go right to the toilet, then go right to the counter, go left to the leftmost sink.
Pick up the bar of soap that is in the sink.
Turn around and go to the toilet.
Put the bar of soap on the back of the toilet.
Turn around and head back to the counter.
Pick up the bar of soap that is between the two sinks.
Turn around and head to the toilet.
Stand the bar of soap up just to the right of the other bar of soap on the back of the toilet.
anns.task_desc: Put two bars of soap on the back of the toilet.

high_descs: Turn right, hang a right at the toilet and walk to the white sink on the left.
Pick up the bar of soap from inside the sink on the vanity.
Turn around to face the white toilet ahead.
Put the bar of soap on the right corner of the toilet tank.
Turn around to face the vanity in between the sinks.
Pick up the bar of soap to the left of the candle on the vanity.
Turn around to face the white toilet.
Put the bar of soap on the right side of the toilet tank behind the other bar of soap.
anns.task_desc: Place two bars of soap on a toilet tank.
